
# # Broken Link Hijacking

There are a lot of possible attacks that can be carried out with broken external links as noted [here](https://gist.github.com/EdOverflow/24e0bb929169eb948bb7f3d0a2d5528f).

In order to hijacking the broken link was required to do a subdomain takeover of the domain **URL**

## Steps To Reproduce


{IMG}

Click on the link as shown in the picture. 

## Impact

The attacker can put malicious content on the taken subdomain.

 
